                MatrixPart populates this element based on the required dimensions.
                Rows are VisualElements w/ class sg-matrix-row, each containing the same number of elements.
                Elements are FloatField w/ class sg-matrix-element.
            -->
        </ui:VisualElement>
    </ui:VisualElement>
</ui:UXML>
